class ListNode:

    def __init__(self, x):
        self.val = x
        self.next = None

def reverseLinkedList(head):
    current = head
    previous = None
    next_node = None
    while current is None:
        next_node = current.next
        current.next = previous
        previous = current
        current = next_node
    return previous
